---
@META
dir: src/components/chapters
updated: 2026-03-18
files: 10
stack: React 18, TypeScript, Tailwind CSS, react-markdown

@EXPORTS
ChapterCard.tsx: ChapterCard — card displaying chapter info, progress stars, completion state
ChapterCard.stories.tsx: ChapterCardStories — Storybook stories
ChapterContent.tsx: ChapterContent — markdown renderer for chapter text content
ChapterHeader.tsx: ChapterHeader — chapter page header with title, number, difficulty badge
ChapterLayout.tsx: ChapterLayout — chapter detail page layout with sidebar navigation
ChapterNavigation.tsx: ChapterNavigation — prev/next chapter navigation buttons
QuestionCard.tsx: QuestionCard — interactive quiz question with answer options & feedback
ProjectSubmission.tsx: ProjectSubmission — form for submitting project URL & description
VideoPlayer.tsx: VideoPlayer — HTML5 video player for chapter video lessons
NotebookLinks.tsx: NotebookLinks — links to Google Colab & NotebookLM resources

@FUNCTIONS
ChapterCard({chapter,progress,completion}) → JSX
  purpose: display chapter card in list with 3-star progress indicators
  side-effects: none
  called-by: chapters list page

QuestionCard({question,chapterId,onAnswer}) → JSX
  purpose: render quiz question, handle answer selection, show explanation
  side-effects: api (POST /api/questions/answer)
  called-by: chapter detail page

ProjectSubmission({chapterId}) → JSX
  purpose: form to submit project URL, calls submit API
  side-effects: api (POST /api/projects/submit)
  called-by: chapter detail page

VideoPlayer({filename}) → JSX
  purpose: stream video from /api/video/[filename]
  side-effects: none
  called-by: chapter detail page

@DEPENDENCIES
internal: @/components/ui, @/data/chapters, @/lib/utils, @/lib/constants
external: react, react-markdown, lucide-react, next/link, next/image

@STANDARDS
- 3-star system: star1=chapter complete, star2=questions answered, star3=project submitted
- Chapter content loaded from public/prednasky/*.md via react-markdown
- Video streamed via API route (not direct file access)
---
